in Exp Res 18 (1994): 761-6[18] Taivainen H, Laitinen K, Tahtela R, Kilanmaa K, Valimaki MJ "Role of plasma vasopressin in changes of water balance accompanying acute alcohol intoxication." Alcohol Clin Exp Res 19 (1995): 759-62', 1767365206);
